1)What is python? What are the ways to install python in your pc?
Python is an interpreted high level language developed by Guido Van Rossum in the year 1991.It became popular in the 2006.
Ways to install python in pc,
1.Anaconda navigator
2.Python IDLE
3.Pycharm

